Project Name: Mnemonic Converter 
 
Outline: Create a cross-platform mobile application that can validate a Mnemonic phrase and convert it from one language to another. 
 
Language & Tools:  
TypeScript 
 
MVP Functionalities: 
Validate mnemonic phrase. 
Convert mnemonic phrase to another language. 
Create algorithm for mapping indexes of Mnemonic phrase during conversion 
 
Extra Functionalities: 
Create frontend UI for mnemonic phrase validation. 
Create frontend UI for mnemonic conversion between supported languages. 
 
